title: #144 - Hila Becomes An American Citizen
description: On this EXTRAORDINARY episode of The H3 Podcast we have a lot to celebrate! Hila became a US Citizen, Zach has been with us for 1 year (and it's his birthday) and we have tons of goofs and gaffs to JUMP RIGHT INTO so, please... enjoy.
